item.description:
Let's meet for karaoke.

This is a multi-meetup group event, not just with the ones that I am an assistant organizer of but also Mark Longworth's Worcester group(s).

Karaoke starts at 8:30.

See www.newtiki.com .

Assistant organizer Neil
item.how_to_find_us: I'll wear my baseball cap that says "NEIL" on it.
item.why: If you like to sing, this is great. If you like to dance or even if you just like to watch and socialize, this is also good.
